# PrusaSlicer

Use [Prusa Knowledge Base](https://help.prusa3d.com/category/prusaslicer_204) as the reference for:

- **Printer Settings**: Retraction, firmware, nozzle profiles, bed models
- **Print Settings**: Layers, perimeters, infill, supports, skirt/brim
- **Filament Settings**: Temperature, flow, bed adhesion
- **Profiles**: Configuration wizard, custom presets

Project layout:
- `slicer/prusa-slicer/printer/` — printer configs
- `slicer/prusa-slicer/process/` — print presets (layer height, speed, etc.)
- `slicer/prusa-slicer/filament/` — material profiles
